CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 23, 1940, pg. 13, reads: "To West Virginia - These charming Pittsburghers, Miss Aline and Miss Ethelyne Frazier will be among those trekking to West Virginia this Saturday, Nov. 23, when W. Va. State College and Wilberforce meet for their annual gridiron clash. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Aline and Ethelyne Frazier seated on floor in front of circular background in Harris Studio
